# This app has no backend and reads no secrets at build time.
#
# The Anthropic API key is entered once inside the app (Settings, key icon) and
# stored only in your browser's local database. It is never bundled, committed, or
# sent anywhere except Anthropic. There is nothing to configure here.
#
# The only optional variable is the default model, baked in at build time:
VITE_ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6
